<section class="section section--42-42-0-72 ai-problems-wrapper">
	<h2>The Problem</h2>
	<p class="mb42">Selecting employee health insurance is often a complicated and time-consuming process for small and medium-sized businesses. Business owners and HR teams must compare multiple providers, evaluate coverage options, understand pricing structures, and balance employee needs with budget constraints. <br><br>The challenge is not finding insurance plans. The challenge is understanding which plan is actually the best fit.</p>
	<h3>As a result, they often experience:</h3>
	<div class="ai-problems">
		<div class="ai-problems__item">
			<div class="circle-label">
				<img src="/assets/img/icons/broom.svg" alt="Information overload icon">
			</div>
			<div>Information <br>overload</div>
		</div>
		<div class="ai-problems__item">
			<div class="circle-label">
				<img src="/assets/img/icons/child.svg" alt="Decision fatigue icon">
			</div>
			<div>Decision <br>fatigue</div>
		</div>
		<div class="ai-problems__item">
			<div class="circle-label">
				<img src="/assets/img/icons/thumbs-down.svg" alt="Uncertainty icon">
			</div>
			<div>Uncertainty about <br>plan quality</div>
		</div>
		<div class="ai-problems__item">
			<div class="circle-label">
				<img src="/assets/img/icons/clock.svg" alt="Lengthy process icon">
			</div>
			<div>Lengthy comparison processes</div>
		</div>
		<div class="ai-problems__item">
			<div class="circle-label">
				<img src="/assets/img/icons/headset.svg" alt="Consultant support icon">
			</div>
			<div>Dependence on <br>external consultants</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<p>
		<b>What if AI could</b> simplify health insurance selection by acting as an intelligent advisor? <br>
		<br>Instead of manually comparing dozens of plans, businesses could receive personalized recommendations based on their workforce, budget, and coverage goals. The objective is not to replace insurance experts. The objective is to help businesses make informed decisions faster and with greater confidence.</p>
</section>

<section class="section section--42-42-0-72 ai-solution-wrapper">
	<h2>Solution</h2>
	<div class="ai-solution">
		<p>This concept allowed me to explore how AI can support complex business decisions in the healthcare benefits space. <br><br> The biggest challenge was designing an experience that balances automation, transparency, and trust while helping organizations make faster and more informed insurance decisions.</p>
		<div>
			<h3>The platform helps businesses:</h3>
			<ul class="ai-solutions">
				<li>
					<img src="/assets/img/icons/check-green.svg" alt="Included capability">
					<span>Define coverage needs</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<img src="/assets/img/icons/check-green.svg" alt="Included capability">
					<span>Discover relevant insurance providers</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<img src="/assets/img/icons/check-green.svg" alt="Included capability">
					<span>Compare plans more efficiently</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<img src="/assets/img/icons/check-green.svg" alt="Included capability">
					<span>Understand recommendation logic</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<img src="/assets/img/icons/check-green.svg" alt="Included capability">
					<span>Make confident enrollment decisions</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

